<TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=12 CELLPADDING=0>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>Is this service really free?</SPAN><BR>Our email service is absolutely free. You will never be charged for using the service.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>I have more than one EverQuest character. Can I sign up for multiple accounts?</SPAN><BR>Yes, you may sign up for multiple email accounts. The email notification feature makes it easy to keep track of when messages arrive in each account.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>What are the rules for choosing a login name?</SPAN><BR>Your login name may contain only letters (a-z), numbers (0-9), the underscore (_) and the period (.). It must start with a letter or number, and cannot be more than 24 characters long.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>The login name I want is taken, what are some alternatives?</SPAN><BR>If your character's name is already taken by another user, you might consider appending your character's surname, guild tag, or server name. Some players opt to use their real-life name.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>How do I change the name that appears on outgoing messages?</SPAN><BR>Click on <B>Options</B> and select <B>Preferences</B>, then change the <B>Name</B> field to anything you wish. This name will appear on messages you send.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>What is the URL of my personal message page?</SPAN><BR>Your personal message page can be found at "http://www.everquestmail.com/message.asp?to=<B>loginname</B>" where <B>loginname</B> is your login name. For more information, visit the <A HREF="message.asp">Personal Message Page</A> area.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>Does the personal information I provide stay private?</SPAN><BR>We are committed to keeping your information safe and secure, and will not reveal your individually identifiable information without your consent. See our <A HREF="http://www.everyone.net/main/html/p_policy.html">Privacy Policy</A> for more details.</TD></TR>
<TR><TD><SPAN CLASS=question>I have an EverQuest web site, how do I link to EverQuest Mail?</SPAN><BR>Visit our <A HREF="link.asp">Link to Us</A> section for image links and text links that you can use on your site.</TD></TR>
